slides.faq.a6.message:
FunBlocks AI Slides focuses on improving efficiency and content quality. Key advantages include: 
1. Quick creation based on Markdown; 
2. AI-assisted content generation and optimization; 
3. Minimalist design, reducing time spent on formatting; 
4. Online collaboration and sharing; 
5. Seamless integration with the FunBlocks ecosystem. 
These features allow you to create high-quality presentations faster, rather than getting bogged down in complex design details.
